mall>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/toBlob\"><code>toBlob()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/toDataURL\"><code>toDataURL()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/transferControlToOffscreen\"><code>transferControlToOffscreen()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/webglcontextlost_event\"><code>webglcontextlost</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Canvas API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasPattern\"><code>CanvasPattern</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmapRenderingContext\"><code>ImageBitmapRenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas\"><code>OffscreenCanvas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/createImageBitmap\"><code>createImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div id=\"sect2\">\n<div id=\"sect3\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>A propriedade&nbsp;<strong><code><span>HTMLCanvasElement.height</span></code></strong>&nbsp;é um&nbsp;<code>inteiro</code>&nbsp;positivo&nbsp;que reflete o atributo <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas#attr-height\"><code>height</code></a> do elemento HTML <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> interpretado em pixels no CSS. Quando o atributo não é especificado, ou se for&nbsp;definido como um valor inválido, como um <code>inteiro</code>&nbsp;negativo, o valor padrão de <code>150</code>&nbsp;será usado.</p>\n\n<p>Essa é uma de duas propriedades, que controla o tamanho do canvas, sendo a outra&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/width\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.width</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>var <em>pxl</em> = <em>canvas</em></var>.height;\n<em>canvas</em>.height = <em>pxl</em>;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dado este elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a>:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>canvas</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>canvas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Você pode capturar a altura do canvas com o seguinte código:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> canvas <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>height<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 300</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/scripting.html#attr-canvas-height\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'HTMLCanvasElement.height' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>No change since the latest snapshot, <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'HTML5' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/scripting-1.html#attr-canvas-height\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'HTMLCanvasElement.height' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/scripting-1.html#attr-canvas-height\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'HTMLCanvasElement.height' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>Snapshot of the <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'HTML Living Standard' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a> containing the initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLCanvasElement.height","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/height/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>A interface a define, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a>.</li>\n <li>Outra propriedade para controlar o tamanho do canvas, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/width\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.width</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"A propriedade HTMLCanvasElement.height é um inteiro positivo que reflete o atributo height do elemento HTML <canvas> interpretado em pixels no CSS. Quando o atributo não é especificado, ou se for definido como um valor inválido, como um inteiro negativo, o valor padrão de 150 será usado.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.height","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.height","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.hei